  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.54,
      "text": "I know y'all were waiting to hear back from me",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 1.54,
      "end": 4.12,
      "text": "on the full-time offer, so I wanted to tell y'all,",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 5.14,
      "end": 8.0,
      "text": "I've decided to stay true to who I really am",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 8.0,
      "end": 11.21,
      "text": "and what I want to do, and I need to dip.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 12.34,
      "end": 14.96,
      "text": "I'm trying to go somewhere that I can reach my full potential",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 14.96,
      "end": 18.52,
      "text": "and take some risks, so I'm joining a startup.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 20.09,
      "end": 20.63,
      "text": "That made your place.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 21.37,
      "end": 21.63,
      "text": "Very sad.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 21.63,
      "end": 21.79,
      "text": "I understand.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 22.57,
      "end": 22.73,
      "text": "Very sad.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 22.97,
      "end": 25.95,
      "text": "And although at times the vibes here were super weak",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 25.95,
      "end": 28.25,
      "text": "and it low-key felt like I was carrying the squad",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2021,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 28.85,
      "end": 31.45,
      "text": "and a full-time offer is a mad disrespect for me.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 34.08,
      "end": 36.18,
      "text": "A dead-ass learned hella from the team here.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 37.06,
      "end": 39.72,
      "text": "And while I won't miss the meetings or the corporate speak,",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 40.3,
      "end": 43.2,
      "text": "I'll miss watching y'all circle back, zoom out,",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 43.66,
      "end": 46.1,
      "text": "piggyback, and even burp your way through the workday.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 47.66,
      "end": 47.74,
      "text": "Right.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 47.9,
      "end": 49.32,
      "text": "While I seek my alignment elsewhere,",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 49.98,
      "end": 51.7,
      "text": "I want to thank y'all for letting me cook here.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 52.32,
      "end": 53.42,
      "text": "It's been wild, for real.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 54.44,
      "end": 55.68,
      "text": "Thank you very much for watching.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 56.02,
      "end": 56.44,
      "text": "Go get them.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 56.82,
      "end": 57.14,
      "text": "They're lucky.",
      "avg_logprob": -0.2722,
      "speaker_turn": 3
    }
  ],
